org.objectstyle.cayenne.gen Contains classes that provide Java source generation facility. 
org.objectstyle.cayenne.map Contains O/R mapping classes that store relational database metadata information and map it to Java classes. 
org.objectstyle.cayenne.map.event   
org.objectstyle.cayenne.project Contains model classes used by CayenneModeler or any other MVC type of application to work with Cayenne project files. 
org.objectstyle.cayenne.project.validator   
org.objectstyle.cayenne.query Provides classes to build database queries in object terms. 
org.objectstyle.cayenne.tools Command line tools and Ant tasks. 
org.objectstyle.cayenne.util General utility classes. 
org.objectstyle.cayenne.wocompat Contains classes that interface Cayenne with Apple's WebObjects.
